parameters: Conspirator Karin: "Fufufu, how foolish. Were you dreaming, perhaps?"

Conspirator Karin: "It seems you haven't realized yet that your belly
has been slashed open."
Katsuhito: "Wha- What are you talking... about?"
Conspirator Karin: "Try to remember what happened to you."
Conspirator Karin: "Power is welling up from the depths of my body."
Katsuhito: "That's... a lie! This is a lie!"
Katsuhito: "...Hm? I don't feel any pain."

Katsuhito: "I'm bleeding this much and yet I feel neither pain nor
itch... Haha, this must be a dream! If it's a dream, wake up already!"
Conspirator Karin: "It should be starting any moment now. Fufufufufu."
Conspirator Karin: "Fufufu, it suits you very well."

Conspirator Karin: "You filthy, stinking piece of trash, Katsuhito-
kun."
Dagnoah: "Karin, well done. It's splendid indeed!"
Conspirator Karin: "Thank you very much, my lord Dagnoah-sama."
Conspirator Karin: "Thanks to you, I have such wonderful power!"
Dagnoah: "You seem to like it quite a bit."
Dagnoah: "Use that power to finish off Pony-Celes."
Dagnoah: "He's an annoying fly that interferes with my plans."
Conspirator Karin: "Of course, it shall be done."
Dagnoah: "Ah, I don't care about the means."

Conspirator Karin: "Understood. I will certainly finish off Pony-
Celes."
Conspirator Karin: "How does it feel to be reborn?"

Conspirator Karin: "That's right, you want to die, don't you? With
such an ugly form, you'd want to die, wouldn't you?"

Conspirator Karin: "Fufu, I could kill you swiftly if you'd like. If
you tell me where Tsukeshiba is."

Conspirator Karin: "You said something about holing up in a lab,
didn't you? Where might that be?"

Conspirator Karin: "I understand. You prefer to stay that way
forever."
Conspirator Karin: "Fufufufufu, I've just had a wonderful idea."

Conspirator Karin: "Tsukeshiba, and Morisaki! I'm about to show you
both hell."
Conspirator Karin: "Oh, did I make such a promise?"

Conspirator Karin: "You think I'd allow you to die? Live on in agony
with that form for the rest of your life."

Thanks to Pony-Celes' efforts, peace was restored to Shoto Academy,
but due to Zaidrag's attack, repairs were needed everywhere.

As an academic institution, concerns about the students' declining
academic performance during the closure prompted rapid repair work,
and most of the school was restored within a week.

The students were excited about the reopening of the school the next
day, but--
One student would disappear on the day the school reopened.
